TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CustomerComplaintDetail.CustomerComplaintDetail_ID, CustomerComplaintDetail.CustomerComplaintID, CustomerComplaintDetail.ComplaintStatus, CustomerComplaintDetail.ComplaintType, CustomerComplaintDetail.ActionType, CustomerComplaintDetail.Description, CustomerComplaintDetail.ShortDescription, CustomerComplaintDetail.IsVehicleOperable, CustomerComplaintDetail.IsTow, CustomerComplaintDetail.ServiceLocationID, CustomerComplaintDetail.CreateDate, CustomerComplaintDetail.ComplaintCloseDate, CustomerComplaintDetail.CreatedByUserID FROM RALLI.[dbo].CustomerComplaintDetail WHERE CustomerComplaintDetail.CreateDate >cast($$v_last_max_date as date)
